title: Southwest Airlines - available seat miles 2011 to 2019
summary: Overall ASMs in billions has increased over the Year.
ASMs in billions is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2012, roughly constant from 2012 to 2014, and lastly gradually increasing from 2014 to 2018.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest ASMs in billions, of value 159.8 was reached at Year 2018
The lowest ASMs in billions, of value 120.58 was reported at Year 2011
